725823f-a.title: Queens: 119th Street - 14th Avenue
725823f-a.text:
119th Street, at the N.E. corner of 14th Avenue (right),
showing the stables and servants' quarters on the A. Hammacher
estate of 1873. The property was owned by F. A. Bogar in 1891.
P. L. Sperr  March 16, 1932

725023f-a.title: Queens: 14th Avenue - 119th Street
725023f-a.text:
14th Avenue, at the S.E. corner of 119th Street, showing
Eshofferts College Point Bar & Grill.
P. L. Sperr  August 5, 1935
